{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_UySN4mZPi50goCEeicV31aAL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这张截图展示了定价页的完整内容：\n- Monthly: $19/mo\n- Annual: $12/mo (billed annually, unlimited access for one year)\n- 功能包含：Host-led group focus sessions, Silent focus space, Access to the community, Member perks and discounts\n- FAQ 部分\n- 页脚有 Product, Resources, Company 链接\n\n现在我有了足够的信息来写报告。让我开始撰写 report.md。\n\n我需要：\n1. 写 report.md（按照 REPORT_TEMPLATE.md 的格式）\n2. 更新 metadata.json\n\n由于产品本身是纯 Web 应用（没有桌面客户端），而且沙盒网络不可用，我需要：\n- mode: web-only（原因是产品仅有 Web 版）\n- warnings: 记录沙盒网络问题和产品无桌面端的事实\n\n让我开始写报告。","signature":""}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":65242,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":65242,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ce9e158-2d7b-4fcc-9acd-2ffab654326b","uuid":"16d17037-a442-4e49-9881-1f908df2e67c"}
